description: Pier 4, located in the heart of Boston’s Seaport, offers an exceptional experience of luxury and coastal life. This stunning 2 bed, 2 bath unit features open-concept living with expansive windows covering the walls, filling the residence with endless natural light and sweeping harbor views. On this 3rd floor unit, the private deck offers a serene and immersive experience of Boston Harbor. Both bedrooms include waterfront views, walk-in closets, and the primary bedroom has a private full bath. The gourmet kitchen features top-tier Gaggenau appliances and a grand, marble waterfall island. Additional features include a storage unit, 1 valet/garage parking, and accessible guest parking unique to the city. The impressive array of amenities also ranges from 24-hr concierge and doorman to a fitness center, owners' lounge, grill, community kitchen, and even a golf simulator. Along with the surrounding dining, shopping, and recreation, Pier 4 delivers a vibrant and elegant lifestyle.
